textBeforeTable: The following large communities are also in the area. Please note that when we give a distance, it's a 'straight-line' distance and not the distance if you drove.<3> The largest community within a 50 mile [80 km] radius is Manhattan. It is located about 24 miles [38 km] to the northeast of where Skiddy would have been located. Manhattan has a population of 56,100 people.<2> The next largest community is Salina. It is located about 44 miles [70 km] to the west of Skiddy and has a population of 47,900 people. Around Skiddy ...
